{"tid":1579254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 香城Online新職業 — 派膠師 (封測中)","createTime":"2019-09-18T13:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T14:18:01.000Z","uid":116509,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7c3ac96cf3e6260143b59ea55ec6ad4fd71e21","tid":1579254,"uid":116509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:19:19.000Z","msg":"唔使講，香城Online最強魔法就一定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近排又見到有三隻水箭龜同3萬隻土狼犬和大狼犬出現係地圖上，好想試下捉喎，有沒咩辦法呢?<br />\n土狼犬和大狼犬的介紹:<br />\n這絕對不是那種你第一眼看到就想摸他肚子的狗，他們性格兇惡剛烈，不了解他們的人真的不可隨便接近，但是如果能捉到一隻土狼犬，那絕對是帥炸了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DYMEVjs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDYMEVjs.jpg&h=d5ff995e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/pet/5oab6v6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fpet%2F5oab6v6.html&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=de933756\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/pet/5oab6v6.html</a><br />\n或者<a href=\"https://wiki.52poke.com/wiki/大狼犬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.52poke.com%2Fwiki%2F%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%BC%E7%8A%AC&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=29ce5bae\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.52poke.com/wiki/大狼犬</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以跪求全能嘅連登大神指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望可以趕得切係黎緊個大型慶典前進行公測<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港  時代革命</span>。<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求  缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"43eb2e0b25876aecacfb46c40753bce714f207a4","tid":1579254,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「9